**Flow Summary**

```
Total: 1,000,000 records
         │
    Read 50k at a time (fetchRecords)
         │
    Split into 5 × 10k chunks
         │
   ┌─────┼─────┬─────┬─────┐
Thread1 Thread2 Thread3 Thread4 Thread5
   │       │      │      │      │
 own DB  own DB  ...   ...   ...
 conn    conn
 own     own
 buffer  buffer
   │       │      │      │      │
  bulkInsert every 1k rows
   └─────┴─────┴─────┴─────┘
         │
    Wait (future.get())
         │
    Next 50k batch
```

---

**What `ThreadLocal` gives you here**

| | Without ThreadLocal | With ThreadLocal |
|---|---|---|
| DB connections | Shared → needs locking | 1 per thread, no contention |
| Result buffer | New list per task | Reused across chunks |
| Transaction scope | Complex coordination | Isolated per thread |

